1508637-a.folder: York Avenue #1393-99 - 74th Street, looking northwest, Manhattan, NY
1508637-a.title: York Avenue #1393-99 - 74th Street, looking northwest

724905f-a.text:
York Ave (Avenue A), west side, looking north from and including East 74th Street. Shown at the N.W. corner of East 74th Street is an
itinerant circus.
September 25, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
